dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n五毛死全家"},{"pid":"9c7b821db4d2999ea8fee483a1167f268c5b331a","tid":769178,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a517fa198966b11609f60f522dd3a4498bf5e4","tid":769178,"uid":51933,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"所以你中共玩到香港咁殘<br />\n<br />\n為乜呢<br />\n蠢撚到豬咁<br />\n<br />\n香港明明係大一舊生金蛋既雞<br />\n偏偏中國式思維就係殺雞取卵<br />\n<br />\n膚淺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"佢地最想要既係面子同全面控制<br />\n人地英國做到，佢地點解做唔到"},{"pid":"f6650b60dde1565807712bbc4c68342289576c5f","tid":769178,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"大紀元係有啲缐眼，曾經俾佢講中左薄熙來。"},{"pid":"47d74ffffbe3acb674d7c5a558bc9751642a61cf","tid":769178,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"之前仲吹到有得揮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}